text: Eleftherios Venizelos (full name Elefthérios Kyriákou Venizélos, ; 23 August 1864 - 18 March 1936) was a Greek politician.Kitromilides, 2006, p. 178'Liberty Still Rules' , Time, Feb. 18, 1924 He was the Prime Minister of Greece from 1910 to 1920 and again from 1928 to 1932. ==References== ==Other websites== Category:1864 births Category:1936 deaths Category:Eastern Orthodox Christians Category:Government ministers of Greece Category:Greek journalists Category:Greek lawyers Category:Prime ministers of Greece Category:Translators
